title: Remember Why You Started At Arras!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 510-530 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Seize the adventure of life at Arras – centrally located in Bellevue’s up-and-coming Spring District.', 'With three buildings around a courtyard, Arras is a vibrant, welcoming community that offers sophisticated details and quality finishes in bright, airy apartment homes.', 'Minutes from downtown Bellevue and a short trip to Seattle attractions, live at the gateway to the Pacific Northwest’s outdoor paradise, with easy access to the slopes, the surf and everything in between.', 'Features:', 'Gas Range *, Full-Size Washer and Dryer, Open Floor Plan, Kitchen Island with Pendant Lighting *, Balcony or Deck *, Stainless Steel Appliances, Designer Finishes, Full-Sized, Quality Appliances, FiberInternet, Direct to Each Apartment, Quartz Countertops', '*Only available in select units', 'Community Amenities:', 'Club Fitness: 2 levels with Peloton, Weights & Cardio, Courtyard with Landscaping, The Hub + The Perch: Gourmet Kitchen, Pedal Club: Game Room with TV & bike Repair Stand, Assigned Parking Available – (additional fee), Permanent Art Installations, EV Charging Stations Available, Sky Deck: Rooftop Deck with Fire Pit, The Lodge: Top-Floor Resident Lounge, Pet Washing Station, Conference Room & Co-Working Spaces, Friendly On-Site Management and Maintenance', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'HjEPXPt2']
